00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:57.000
With VS Code, people just love that it's extremely customizable.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.000
Again, multilingual, AI-equipped.

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:03.000
We took the best of both worlds, and we made Positron.

