That's Positron, but today's focus is really about highlighting some of the really cool AI LLM integrations with Positron.

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:17.000
The first one that we're going to introduce you to is something called Positron Assistant.

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:22.000
This is an AI client that's actually built directly into Positron.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.000
